This is the help file for pupRadio/Telly.
Just find audio or video streams on the web and save as a Preset 
or a Bookmark, don't forget to give it a name.
You can test a stream before saving with the "Play Now!" feature.
If you get Precord from 
http://www.murga-linux.com/puppy/viewtopic.php?t=49907
You can even record, follow instructions on that thread.
Pupradio now works from the command line. It plays the last
radio station you played from the GUI. Telly is unsupported.# Very End of this file 'usr/local/pupradio/help' #
###END###
